
  Plot Manipulation Procedures from Astronomical Users' Library (Nov 1993)

    CLEANPLOT   :   Reset all system variables (!P,!X,!Y,!Z) set by the user 
                    which affect plotting to their default values
    LEGEND      :   Make a legend for a plot
    LEGENDTEST  :   Test the legend procedure
    OPLOTERR    :   Over-plot data points with accompanying X or Y error bars
    PLOTERR     :   Plot data points with accompanying X or Y error bars
    PLOTHIST    :   Plot the histogram of an array with the corresponding 
                    abcissa
    PLOTSYM     :   Define useful plotting symbols not in the standard !PSYM 
                    definitions
    PLOT_KEYWORDS : Return default value(s) of plotting keywords

